data.description: Motivated Seller! This Stunning 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhome is in the desirable & established subdivision of Madison Place in Davenport, Florida. Upon entry, you are greeted with a beautiful and welcoming foyer drawing you into the Open Kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances that pair perfectly with the trimmed cabinets. The large open space flows directly into your bright living room and is flooded with natural light coming from the large windows and the Sliding Glass Door which leads out to your Spacious Backyard. Out back you have 6' High Vinyl Fencing for privacy. As you make your way back inside and up to the second level, you will pass the Half Baths that is located under the stairs which is perfect for keeping your guest on the main floor. Upstairs you will find the remaining Sizable Bedrooms and Bathrooms along with a conveniently placed Laundry room. You will also find the wonderful Master Bedroom which is large enough for a King Sized bed and additional large furniture with room to spare! Inside the Master Bathroom will lead you to your Huge Walk-in closet. This home is located right on Highway 27, providing Easy Access to Advent Health Hospital, outdoor shopping, and a plethora of restaurants. Plus, it's Only 30-40 minutes from Disney , Universal SeaWorld and all the major attractions ! The community offers a beautiful Playground for the family and an Amazing Pool for you to enjoy. Don't wait to call this place HOME!
